{"tid":689762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港法庭係咪圖書館之外最多精神病人既聚腳點？","createTime":"2018-06-04T10:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T13:28:16.000Z","uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a5523aadeb543002c9b50639b831058f86639824","tid":689762,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"最近個大陸婆影相撚狗晒名唔多講<br />\n特登google下，原來法庭經常吸引左唔少痴線佬聽審<br />\n<br />\n法 庭 怪 客 實 錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20061228/2_6659193/法-庭-怪-客-實-錄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20061228%2F2_6659193%2F%E6%B3%95-%E5%BA%AD-%E6%80%AA-%E5%AE%A2-%E5%AF%A6-%E9%8C%84&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=a57d7fe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20061228%2F2_6659193%2F%E6%B3%95-%E5%BA%AD-%E6%80%AA-%E5%AE%A2-%E5%AF%A6-%E9%8C%84&h=cb4ae139\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20061228/2_6659193/法-庭-怪-客-實-錄</a><br />\n(聽講當年高登好出名個位大大師兄係其中一人)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20090425/20090425022630_0000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fnews%2F20090425%2F20090425022630_0000.html&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=cc89bbcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20090425/20090425022630_0000.html</a><br />\n「自學法律」青年大鬧法庭<br />\n旁聽市民當中，也有一些較為「另類」的例子。本案自開審起，已有一名二十餘歲的男子，每天穿幵白恤衫、黑西褲及結領帶，準時到庭抄寫筆記。某日他更將一封信交給辯方大律師，大律師立刻向法官報告。法官查問他身份，起初他聲稱為法律學生及大律師，經追問下他才坦承自己是「自學法律」。法官並無公開信件內容，但就指摘該名男子的行為可能構成干預審訊，警告他不可再犯。豈料過數日後，此君又再發難，在庭上忽然起立，說控辯雙方的大律師都「唔識打官司」，結果遭法官驅逐離庭，此後便再不見其蹤影。<br />\n<br />\n男子庭內亮刀高呼「無法無天」 警方2度搜查無蹤影<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1926513/男子庭內亮刀高呼「無法無天」%20警方2度搜查無蹤影\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1926513%2F%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%BA%AD%E5%85%A7%E4%BA%AE%E5%88%80%E9%AB%98%E5%91%BC%E3%80%8C%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%84%A1%E5%A4%A9%E3%80%8D%2520%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B92%E5%BA%A6%E6%90%9C%E6%9F%A5%E7%84%A1%E8%B9%A4%E5%BD%B1&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c1228c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1926513/男子庭內亮刀高呼「無法無天」%20警方2度搜查無蹤影</a>"},{"pid":"1df71e5e790d01d1bcc74f7827b4ceafe8e27db3","tid":689762,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a647721dc864f570a8f9a4704deed7da6c7462a","tid":689762,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"有一堆人日日法庭打躉 D官咩性格都記得晒 冇讀法律但睇得多熟晒法律程序 佢哋日日係法庭做筆記但係唔知為乜"},{"pid":"087b9701b84a0c9119629bd70417bc1165d712cf","tid":689762,"uid":43042,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"連登先係"},{"pid":"3b97ab06287f2816fa7e1838e7bfcb2fe96ba9ae","tid":689762,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"巴膠之後又多個精神病品種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab957e9dbae82c1922bf15b648781a0b86e1ba","tid":689762,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b97ab06287f2816fa7e1838e7bfcb2fe96ba9ae","tid":689762,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"巴膠之後又多個精神病品種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"巴膠起碼叫有正常興趣<br />\n呢班友想扮法律專家但又扮得唔似，唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"383f35196cde5053eec1fa67879f353ca3f9149f","tid":689762,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a647721dc864f570a8f9a4704deed7da6c7462a","tid":689762,"uid":52605,"like":0,"di